summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation for the widening of 5th Avenue North under Ordinance 100337, King County Cause No. 746324; authorizing deposit into court of Sixty Thousand Dollars ($60,000) in connection with a right of immediate entry to be granted the City as to Parcel 2, authorizing payment of such deposit from sums heretofore appropriated by Ordinance 100183 for property acquisition for said project and partially superseding Ordinance 100183.
